00:28:32,667 --> 00:28:35,189
So you can add items with a priority.

498
00:28:35,490 --> 00:28:37,591
And then every day when directors meet,

499
00:28:38,252 --> 00:28:41,454
we sort by priority, sort by date, and just boom, boom, boom,

