00:28:52,007 --> 00:28:56,410
rinse and repeat. So we're adding stuff to this document daily and talking about it daily.

506
00:28:59,413 --> 00:29:03,517
The next piece of feedback we got, our next problem we wanted to solve,

507
00:29:04,878 --> 00:29:12,965
was that we had a horrible, horrible feedback process. It was the worst. Let's talk about why

