00:33:33,962 --> 00:33:36,724
cards in the columns, and then you can move the cards around the different columns.

571
00:33:37,044 --> 00:33:42,147
So the first two columns are for anyone to put feedback whenever they want.

572
00:33:42,388 --> 00:33:46,830
There's one column for very important feedback, and one column for everything else.

573
00:33:47,870 --> 00:33:50,412
Then a couple of times a week, I will go through the board

574
00:33:50,572 --> 00:33:52,714
and I would grab everything in that column.

575
00:33:53,555 --> 00:33:56,537
And again, put it in the little box.

576
00:33:56,878 --> 00:33:58,199
I'm going to go and I'm going to think,

577
00:33:59,420 --> 00:34:01,402
what does this feedback want to be?

